    "name": "CRTX - A Psychological Horror Puzzle",
    "steam_appid": 3309870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309870/extras/19d08cd3dc55653bfa5f968b65b47d14.avif?t=1752228046\" width=800 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a strange padded cell with children's music playing and a robotic voice speaking to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You should definitely take the psychological tests it demands, because as little humanity as there is in its voice, there is just as little in its treatment of test subjects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps it would be better to look for a way out...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it's best to do so unnoticed...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve psychologically rich puzzles in an oppressive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think outside the box and prepare for confusing and frightening puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover where you are and how to escape in a mind-bending story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silence the voice forever!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309870/extras/823efe2881cc9e97dd11a7e311e4f722.avif?t=1752228046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309870/extras_big/823efe2881cc9e97dd11a7e311e4f722.avif?t=1752228046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
